---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
import Header from "../components/layout/Header.astro";
import Footer from "../components/layout/Footer.astro";
---

<Layout>
	<Header />
	<main class="py-16 lg:py-24 bg-white">
		<div class="px-6 md:px-10 lg:px-16 max-w-3xl mx-auto">
			<h1 class="text-heading-section text-kfood-primary mb-8">Terms of Service</h1>

			<div class="legal-content space-y-8 font-body text-kfood-body">
				<section>
					<h2 class="text-xl font-heading font-semibold text-kfood-primary mb-3">1. Use of Website</h2>
					<p class="leading-relaxed">
						Permission is granted to temporarily view and download materials on KFood's website for personal, non-commercial use only. You may not modify, copy, or use any content for commercial purposes without our express written consent.
					</p>
				</section>

				<section>
					<h2 class="text-xl font-heading font-semibold text-kfood-primary mb-3">2. Account Responsibility</h2>
					<p class="leading-relaxed">
						If you create an account on our website, you are responsible for maintaining the confidentiality of your account details and password. You agree to provide accurate and current information for all purchases made at our store.
					</p>
				</section>

				<section>
					<h2 class="text-xl font-heading font-semibold text-kfood-primary mb-3">3. Product Specifications and Pricing</h2>
					<p class="leading-relaxed">
						Prices for our products are subject to change without notice. We reserve the right to modify or discontinue any product or service at any time. We shall not be liable to you or any third party for any price changes, modifications, or discontinuance of products.
					</p>
				</section>

				<section>
					<h2 class="text-xl font-heading font-semibold text-kfood-primary mb-3">4. Accuracy of Information</h2>
					<p class="leading-relaxed">
						We reserve the right to correct any errors and inaccuracies.
					</p>
				</section>

				<section>
					<h2 class="text-xl font-heading font-semibold text-kfood-primary mb-3">5. Returns and Cancellations</h2>
					<p class="leading-relaxed">
						Customers must report any damaged or incorrect items within 24 hours of delivery to be eligible for a replacement or refund.
					</p>
				</section>
			</div>

			<p class="mt-12 font-body text-muted text-sm">
				Last updated: February 2025. For questions, contact us at <a href="mailto:contact@kfood.pk" class="text-kfood-primary underline">contact@kfood.pk</a>.
			</p>
		</div>
	</main>
	<Footer />
</Layout>
